[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1862[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1863[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1864[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the assistant occasionally claims state it has no source for, drifts into adjacent-pathway scope without routing, presents caregiver-only information to patients or vice versa, proposes care-team alerts the institution does not actually want generated, or produces tone-inappropriate responses for the patient or caregiver. The output-safety pipeline is the audit-and-trust floor of the assistant; the institutional review process specifically tags failure modes by category for continuous improvement.
